OL,3,CConsumer expectations for economy
OL,4,Cplunge to 'new low'
OL,6,FConsumer expectations for the economy
OL,7,Fhave plunged to a new low as the
OL,8,FGovernment faces continued pressure
OL,9,Fover public finances, a survey shows.
OL,11,FExpectations for the state of the
OL,12,Feconomy over the next three months
OL,13,Fhave worsened to a figure of minus 34,
OL,14,Fdown from minus 27 in December,
OL,15,Faccording to the British Retail
OL,16,FConsortium (BRC) Consumer Sentiment
OL,17,FMonitor.
