OL,6,FThose aged 18 to 27 ` Generation Z `
OL,7,Fremain the only group to expect the
OL,8,Feconomy to improve, while two-thirds
OL,9,Fof those aged between 60 and 78 expect
OL,10,Fit to worsen, the poll found.
OL,12,FConfidence in personal finances also
OL,13,Ffell one point to minus four, with
OL,14,Folder generations again remaining the
OL,15,Fmost pessimistic.
