OL,6,FExpectations of retail spending and
OL,7,Fwider spending both fell
OL,8,Fsignificantly, although the BRC said
OL,9,Fmuch of the drop is likely to be a
OL,10,Freflection of the end of the Christmas
OL,11,Fperiod as people "tightened their
OL,12,Fbelts for the new year ahead".
OL,14,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,15,Fsaid: "As the Government warns of
OL,16,Ftough times ahead, it is little
OL,17,Fsurprise that the public have caught
OL,18,Fthe January blues.
