OL,6,F"Consumer confidence in the economy
OL,7,Ffell to a new low, with concerns most
OL,8,Fpronounced among older generations."
OL,10,FShe added: "On top of this challenging
OL,11,Fmarket backdrop, retailers are facing
OL,12,F#7 billion in additional costs from
OL,13,Fthe Budget and new packaging levy.
OL,15,F"With retailers' tight margins leaving
OL,16,Flittle scope to absorb more costs,
OL,17,Fmany are warning of price rises and
OL,18,Fjob cuts in the coming months.
