OL,6,F"To mitigate this, and shore up
OL,7,Finvestment in shops and entry level
OL,8,Fjobs, the Government must ensure that
OL,9,Fno shop ends up paying a higher
OL,10,Fbusiness rates bill because of its
OL,11,Fproposed reforms."
OL,13,FThe survey follows volatility in the
OL,14,FUK Government bond market at the start
OL,15,Fof the year, which sent public sector
OL,16,Fborrowing costs soaring and led to
OL,17,Ffears that Chancellor Rachel Reeves is
OL,18,Fon track to miss her fiscal rules.
